21. 不同的用语，不同的结果：为什么语言可以或好或坏的改变人生

https://fenxiao.xiaoe-tech.com/#/try_page/1/apprToXjJCE2967/a_5b63b4c94b29b_ebren0KA

<section style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 10px 0%; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; width: 100%; vertical-align: top; padding: 15px; background-position: 25.8037% -43.1473%; background-repeat: repeat; background-size: 29.7866%; background-attachment: scroll; box-shadow: rgb(0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px; background-image: url(&#39;http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/apprToXjJCE2967/image/ueditor/41040000_1523329595.png&#39;); box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">在日常工作与生活中，<span style="font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">我们</span>很容易陷入各种沟通困局中：</p></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="width: 1.4em; height: 1.4em; border-radius: 100%; transform: rotate(0deg); -webkit-transform: rotate(0deg); -moz-transform: rotate(0deg); -o-transform: rotate(0deg); line-height: 1.5em; float: left; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(249, 110, 87); color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="clear: none; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">沟</p></section><section style="width: 1.4em; height: 1.4em; border-radius: 100%; transform: rotate(0deg); -webkit-transform: rotate(0deg); -moz-transform: rotate(0deg); -o-transform: rotate(0deg); line-height: 1.5em; float: right; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(249, 110, 87); color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="clear: none; margin-to