e="clear: none; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">正</p></section><section style="width: 1.4em; height: 1.4em; border-radius: 100%; transform: rotate(0deg); -webkit-transform: rotate(0deg); -moz-transform: rotate(0deg); -o-transform: rotate(0deg); line-height: 1.5em; float: right; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(249, 110, 87); color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="clear: none; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">面</p></section><section style="clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"></section></section><section style="padding: 0px 0.6em; margin-bottom: -0.8em; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="border: 1px solid rgb(160, 160, 160); padding: 3px; display: inline-block; width: 100%; margin-top: -0.8em; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="width: 100%; border: 1px solid rgb(160, 160, 160); padding: 10px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">▫觉察谈话出现问题时的信号，避免谈话变得无法挽救</span><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">▫提升沟通的有效性，并增加有效沟通的次数</p></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="width: 1.4em; height: 1.4em; border-radius: 100%; line-height: 1.5em; float: left; text-align: center; transform: rotate(0deg); -webkit-transform: rotate(0deg); -moz-transform: rotate(0deg); -o-transform: rotate(0deg); background-color: rgb(249, 110, 87); color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="clear: none; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">沟</p></section><section style="width: 1.4em; height: 1.4em; bor