17. 坚持对话的主线，别被无用分支干扰：如何关注于当下的对话中

https://fenxiao.xiaoe-tech.com/#/try_page/1/apprToXjJCE2967/a_5b63b4c94b0f5_fAwAnGyN

<section style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 10px 0%; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; width: 100%; vertical-align: top; padding: 15px; background-position: 25.8037% -43.1473%; background-repeat: repeat; background-size: 29.7866%; background-attachment: scroll; box-shadow: rgb(0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px; background-image: url(&#39;http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/apprToXjJCE2967/image/ueditor/41040000_1523329595.png&#39;); box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">在日常工作与生活中，<span style="font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">我们</span>很容易陷入各种沟通困局中：</p></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="width: 1.4em; height: 1.4em; border-radius: 100%; transform: rotate(0deg); -webkit-transform: rotate(0deg); -moz-transform: rotate(0deg); -o-transform: rotate(0deg); line-height: 1.5em; float: left; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(249, 110, 87); color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="clear: none; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">沟</p></section><section style="width: 1.4em; height: 1.4em; border-radius: 100%; transform: rotate(0deg); -webkit-transform: rotate(0deg); -moz-transform: rotate(0deg); -o-transform: rotate(0deg); line-height: 1.5em; float: right; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(249, 110, 87); color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="clear: none; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">通</p></section><section style="clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"></section></section><section style="padding: 0px 0.6em; margin-bottom: -0.8em; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="border: 1px solid rgb(160, 160, 160); padding: 3px; display: inline-block; width: 100%; margin-top: -0.8em; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="width: 100%; border: 1px solid rgb(160, 160, 160); padding: 10px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="font-size: 14px; color: rgb(81, 80, 79); box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-family: PingFangTC-light; box-sizing: border-box;">▫你希望和另一半开诚布公地谈一谈，却演变成无法收场的争吵</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-family: PingFangTC-light; box-sizing: border-box;">▫青春期的女儿对你的好意提醒并不领情</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-family: PingFangTC-light; box-sizing: border-box;">▫工作会议仅仅是在浪费时间，因为没人在听别人讲话</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-family: PingFangTC-light; box-sizing: border-box;">▫你主动和同事聊天，却意外地让他对你起了戒心</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-family: PingFangTC-light; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></span></p><p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-family: PingFangTC-light; box-sizing: border-box;">...</span></p></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="width: 1.4em; height: 1.4em; border-radius: 100%; line-height: 1.5em; float: left; text-align: center; transform: rotate(0deg); -webkit-transform: rotate(0deg); -moz-transform: rotate(0deg); -o-transform: rotate(0deg); background-color: rgb(249, 110, 87); color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="clear: none; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">困</p></section><section style="width: 1.4em; height: 1.4em; border-radius: 100%; line-height: 1.5em; float: right; text-align: center; transform: rotate(0deg); -webkit-transform: rotate(0deg); -moz-transform: rotate(0deg); -o-transform: rotate(0deg); background-color: rgb(249, 110, 87); color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="clear: none; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">局</p></section><section style="clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"></section></section></section></section><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">而避免沟通困局的有效方法是提高正面沟通的能力，作者对于正面沟通提出以下两个关键节点：</p></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="width: 1.4em; height: 1.4em; border-radius: 100%; transform: rotate(0deg); -webkit-transform: rotate(0deg); -moz-transform: rotate(0deg); -o-transform: rotate(0deg); line-height: 1.5em; float: left; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(249, 110, 87); color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="clear: none; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">正</p></section><section style="width: 1.4em; height: 1.4em; border-radius: 100%; transform: rotate(0deg); -webkit-transform: rotate(0deg); -moz-transform: rotate(0deg); -o-transform: rotate(0deg); line-height: 1.5em; float: right; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(249, 110, 87); color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="clear: none; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">面</p></section><section style="clear: both; box-sizing: border-box;"></section></section><section style="padding: 0px 0.6em; margin-bottom: -0.8em; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="border: 1px solid rgb(160, 160, 160); padding: 3px; display: inline-block; width: 100%; margin-top: -0.8em; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="width: 100%; border: 1px solid rgb(160, 160, 160); padding: 10px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">▫觉察谈话出现问题时的信号，避免谈话变得无法挽救</span><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">▫提升沟通的有效性，并增加有效沟通的次数</p></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="width: 1.4em; height: 1.4em; border-radius: 100%; line-height: 1.5em; float: left; text-align: center; transform: rotate(0deg); -webkit-transform: rotate(0deg); -moz-transform: rotate(0deg); -o-transform: rotate(0deg); background-color: rgb(249, 110, 87); color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="clear: none; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">沟</p></section><section style="width: 1.4em; height: 1.4em; bor