 padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">这本书怎么用</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">第2章　对话中的各种信号</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">如何发现沟通出问题了</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">警示灯</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">看见信号</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">第3章　保留事情的原貌，切忌添油加醋</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">我们为什么会有负面的想法，如何避免将情况变糟</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">第4章　别在不重要的事情上过分纠缠</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">如何防止微不足道的对话变成不可收场的争论</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">第5章　读懂话语背后的暗示</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">如何理解人们真正想说的话</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">第6章　倾听，别急着张嘴</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">为什么随便听听会导致肤浅的关系</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">第7章　如何处理对话中的负面情绪和思想</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">第8章　不要尝试给对方出主意</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">第9章　换个角度看问题</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">我心胸狭窄吗</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">采用第二和第三视角</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">第10章　分歧再大的对话都能达成某些共识</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">在家里拥有共识</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">第11章　仔细考虑一句话的来龙去脉</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">如何防止误解和有戒心的回答</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">第12章　学会说“对不起”，整理混乱的局面</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">何说对不起并消除分歧</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">第13章　小心祸从口出</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">你可以从人们说话的方式中学到什么</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">第14章　学会提问，对方的需求是问出来的</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">如何避免指责</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">像设计师一样批评</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">领导力的基础</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">第15章　清晰表达，并保证对方正确理解</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">为什么检查信息对称可以节约你的时间、精力和 金钱</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">困惑的成本</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">第16章　坚持对话的主线，别被无用分支干扰</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">第17章　在对话中做做实验</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">如何改变你的对话以恢复对方的关系</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">第18章　讲故事能促进对话</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">如何更有技巧地使用故事并了解他人</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">第19章　有些话不能憋在心里，学会表达</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">如何发现你的声音，并且大声说出想说的话</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">第20章　不同的用语，不同的结果</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">为什么语言可以或好或坏地改变人生</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">第21章　沟通是需要毕生学习的艺术</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">为什么练习比完美更重要</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">消除错误观点</span></p></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; text-align: center; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="width: 40px; height: 5px; line-height: 5px; text-align: right; margin-left: auto; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; vertical-align: middle; width: 30px; border-top: 1px solid rgb(249, 110, 87); border-right-color: rgb(249, 110, 87); border-bottom-color: rgb(249, 110, 87); border-left-color: rgb(249, 110, 87); box-sizing: border-box;"></section><section style="width: 5px; height: 5px; border-radius: 50%; display: inline-block; vertical-align: middle; background-color: rgb(249, 110, 87); box-sizing: border-box;"></section></section><section style="padding-left: 8px; padding-right: 8px; color: rgb(81, 80, 79); box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">作者简介</strong></p></section><section style="width: 40px; height: 5px; line-height: 5px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="width: 5px; height: 5px; border-radius: 50%; display: inline-block; vertical-align: middle; background-color: rgb(249, 110, 87); box-sizing: border-box;"></section><section style="display: inline-block; vertical-align: middle; width: 30px; border-top: 1px solid rgb(249, 110, 87); border-right-color: rgb(249, 110, 87); border-bottom-color: rgb(249, 110, 87); border-left-color: rgb(249, 110, 87); box-sizing: border-box;"></section></section></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 10px 0%; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; width: 100%; vertical-align: top; padding: 15px; background-position: 25.8037% -43.1473%; background-repeat: repeat; background-size: 29.7866%; background-attachment: scroll; background-image: url(&#39;http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/apprToXjJCE2967/image/ueditor/41040000_1523329595.png&#39;); box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="font-size: 15px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(81, 80, 79); box-sizing: border-box;">罗布·肯德尔（Rob Kendall）</span></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(81, 80, 79); box-sizing: border-box;">▫肯德尔是一位非常受人尊敬的管理顾问和沟通领域的权威人士。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(81, 80, 79); box-sizing: border-box;">▫他在沟通领域拥有超过29年的培训经验，为许多国际知名公司，包括美国运通、法国兴业银行和苏黎世银行业的高层做过沟通和变革管理方面的教练。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(81, 80, 79); box-sizing: border-box;">▫肯德尔在知名媒体均设有专栏，包括《今日心理学》（Psychology Today）, 《智族》（GQ）和 《心理月刊》（Psychologies）等。</span></p></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; text-align: center; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="width: 40px; height: 5px; line-height: 5px; text-align: right; margin-left: auto; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; vertical-align: middle; width: 30px; border-top: 1px solid rgb(249, 110, 87); border-right-color: rgb(249, 110, 87); border-bottom-color: rgb(249, 110, 87); border-left-color: rgb(249, 110, 87); box-sizing: border-box;"></section><section style="width: 5px; height: 5px; border-radius: 50%; display: inline-block; vertical-align: middle; background-color: rgb(249, 110, 87); box-sizing: border-box;"></section></section><section style="padding-left: 8px; padding-right: 8px; color: rgb(81, 80, 79); box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">适合谁听</strong></p></section><section style="width: 40px; height: 5px; line-height: 5px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="width: 5px; height: 5px; border-radius: 50%; display: inline-block; vertical-align: middle; background-color: rgb(249, 110, 87); box-sizing: border-box;"></section><section style="display: inline-block; vertical-align: middle; width: 30px; border-top: 1px solid rgb(249, 110, 87); border-right-color: rgb(249, 110, 87); border-bottom-color: rgb(249, 110, 87); border-left-color: rgb(249, 110, 87); box-sizing: border-box;"></section></section></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 10px 0%; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; width: 100%; vertical-align: top; padding: 15px; background-position: 2