同的结果</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">为什么语言可以或好或坏地改变人生</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">第21章　沟通是需要毕生学习的艺术</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">为什么练习比完美更重要</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">消除错误观点</span></p></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; text-align: center; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="width: 40px; height: 5px; line-height: 5px; text-align: right; margin-left: auto; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; vertical-align: middle; width: 30px; border-top: 1px solid rgb(249, 110, 87); border-right-color: rgb(249, 110, 87); border-bottom-color: rgb(249, 110, 87); border-left-color: rgb(249, 110, 87); box-sizing: border-box;"></section><section style="width: 5px; height: 5px; border-radius: 50%; display: inline-block; vertical-align: middle; background-color: rgb(249, 110, 87); box-sizing: border-box;"></section></section><section style="padding-left: 8px; padding-right: 8px; color: rgb(81, 80, 79); box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">作者简介</strong></p></section><section style="width: 40px; height: 5px; line-height: 5px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="width: 5px; height: 5px; border-radius: 50%; display: inline-block; vertical-align: middle; background-color: rgb(249, 110, 87); box-sizing: border-box;"></sec