-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">第8章　不要尝试给对方出主意</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">第9章　换个角度看问题</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">我心胸狭窄吗</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">采用第二和第三视角</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">第10章　分歧再大的对话都能达成某些共识</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">在家里拥有共识</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">第11章　仔细考虑一句话的来龙去脉</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">如何防止误解和有戒心的回答</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">第12章　学会说“对不起”，整理混乱的局面</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">何说对不起并消除分歧</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">第13章　小心祸从口出</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">你可以从人们说话的方式中学到什么</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">第14章　学会提问，对方的需求是问出来的</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">如何避免指责</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">像设计师一样批评</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">领导力的基础</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">第15章　清晰表达，并保证对方正确理解</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">为什么检查信息对称可以节约你的时间、精力和 金钱</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">困惑的成本</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">第16章　坚持对话的主线，别被无用分支干扰</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">第17章　在对话中做做实验</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">如何改变你的对话以恢复对方的关系</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">第18章　讲故事能促进对话</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">如何更有技巧地使用故事并了解他人</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">第19章　有些话不能憋在心里，学会表达</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">如何发现你的声音，并且大声说出想说的话</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">第20章　不同的用语，不同的结果</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">为什么语言可以或好或坏地改变人生</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">第21章　沟通是需要毕生学习的艺术</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">为什么练习比完美更重要</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">消除错误观点</span></p></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; text-align: center; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="width: 40px; height: 5px; line-height: 5px; text-align: right; margin-left: auto; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; vertical-align: middle; width: 30px; border-top: 1px solid rgb(249, 110, 87); border-right-color: rgb(249, 110, 87); border-bottom-color: rgb(249, 110, 87); border-left-color: rgb(249, 110, 87); box-sizing: border-box;"></section><section style="width: 5px; height: 5px; border-radius: 50%; display: inline-block; vertical-align: middle; background-color: rgb(249, 110, 87); box-sizing: border-box;"></section></section><section style="padding-left: 8px; padding-right: 8px; color: rgb(81, 80, 79); box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">作者简介</strong></p></section><section style="width: 40px; height: 5px; line-height: 5px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="width: 5px; height: 5px; border-radius: 50%; display: inline-block; vertical-align: middle; background-color: rgb(249, 110, 87); box-sizing: border-box;"></sec